flowchart TB
    %% Integrity Sentinel - Enterprise Integrity Graph
    %% Purpose: Show how enterprise entities are connected for relationship intelligence.

    EMP["Employee"]
    MGR["Manager"]
    DEPT["Department"]
    VENDOR["Vendor"]
    APPROVAL["Approval"]
    TXN["Transaction"]
    NOM["Nomination / Request"]
    DEVICE["Device"]
    IDENTITY["Identity Account"]
    DOC["Document / Evidence"]
    CASE["Investigation Case"]
    ALERT["Risk Alert"]

    EMP -->|reports_to| MGR
    EMP -->|belongs_to| DEPT
    MGR -->|manages| DEPT

    EMP -->|submits| NOM
    NOM -->|approved_by| APPROVAL
    MGR -->|performs| APPROVAL
    APPROVAL -->|authorizes| TXN

    TXN -->|paid_to / associated_with| VENDOR
    EMP -->|related_to| VENDOR
    VENDOR -->|linked_to| DOC

    EMP -->|uses| DEVICE
    DEVICE -->|associated_with| IDENTITY
    IDENTITY -->|accesses / modifies| DOC

    NOM -->|generates| DOC
    TXN -->|generates| DOC
    APPROVAL -->|generates| DOC

    ALERT -->|references| EMP
    ALERT -->|references| VENDOR
    ALERT -->|references| TXN
    ALERT -->|references| APPROVAL
    ALERT -->|references| NOM
    ALERT -->|references| DOC

    CASE -->|contains| ALERT
    CASE -->|collects| DOC
    CASE -->|investigates| EMP
    CASE -->|investigates| VENDOR
    CASE -->|investigates| TXN

    classDef entity fill:#0f172a,stroke:#38bdf8,color:#e0f2fe,stroke-width:1px;
    classDef risk fill:#312e81,stroke:#a78bfa,color:#ede9fe,stroke-width:1px;
    classDef evidence fill:#1e293b,stroke:#94a3b8,color:#f8fafc,stroke-width:1px;

    class EMP,MGR,DEPT,VENDOR,APPROVAL,TXN,NOM,DEVICE,IDENTITY entity;
    class ALERT,CASE risk;
    class DOC evidence;